snippet.title: Butterfly's Poison; Blood Chains | Opening Movie | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
A love tale of light and shadow set in the Taisho era.

■Product Information
Title : Butterfly's Poison; Blood Chains
Genre : Visual Novel
Platform : Nintendo Switch System / Nintendo Switch Lite system
Store : Nintendo eShop
Release Date : November 11, 2022
Price : USD 44.99 / CAD 59.99 / 44,99 EUR
Rating : ESRB Mature 17+ / PEGI 16 / USK 16 / CERO D

■Cast
Junichi Shiba VA: Chasuke
Mizuhito Nomiya VA: Tatsuya Hirai
Yoshiki Majima VA: Keizo Oishi
Hitoshi Fujita VA: Sandayu Chianoze
Hideo Ozaki VA: Kiya Suga
Kyoko Amami VA: Nekomiai
